= Some Mornings Are Easier When You Don't Have to Guide Yourself

#mcr-lead[Writing suits some mornings. Listening suits others. Both are valid ways to begin.]

The reset in this guide is written on purpose — putting a few words on paper
helps many people hear themselves think. But some mornings you may not feel like
reading or writing at all, and that is completely normal.

On those mornings, some people prefer to be guided by audio instead. There is
nothing wrong with either choice; they simply suit different days.

#mcr-audiowave()

#block(above: 8pt, below: 10pt, mcr-cards(cols: 2, (
